entries.femaleVariant: Fuck. I guess I coulda seen that coming.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="¡Mierda!" b="" a=" How the hell'd you get in here?!"/>
Nolan Frakes sent me.
Dunno. Her father sent me.
What went down, then?
All right – what happened?
A mass, eh? Padre honestly thinks that'll help?
Dunno. Father sent me.
Did this to yourself.
And a lover who wanted to snuggle up to her insurance payout. Touching.
You wanted the insurance payout.
Nolan Frakes sent me.
Hey, Martha's in a coma! Might never wake up! Every goddamn day in that hospital costs me eddies.
Loving father of hers, the one she ran away from – can't even let it go now.
Asshole doesn't even know what went down.
Gonks from 6th Street happened. Fucking ambush.
Were comin' back from a party with Chichex. Pretty smashed. They got us down on Berkeley Avenue. I mean, I was fast, but... they shot faster.
Tryna zero me, got Martha. End of story.
You here to do me too, huh? Do it! Just shoot straight this time, eh? Don't hit no more innocent bystanders.
Not shooting anybody. I believe you.
Why'd they wanna wipe you?
Nobody's shootin' anybody. Believe you.
entries.maleVariant: Nobody's shootin' anyone. I believe you.

entries.femaleVariant: 6th Street. Why'd they wanna wipe you?
I don't-- Can't fuckin' stand 'Tinos?
Martha wasn't s'posed to be there. And 6th Street, huh? Knew I was headed that way. Shit was like a firing squad.
Or maybe someone's got a beef with me, eh? Big enough that he's gotta hire extra iron?
Nolan? C'mon, wouldn't risk his little girl's life for you.
entries.maleVariant: Nolan? C'mon... He wouldn't risk his little girl's life for you.

entries.femaleVariant: So you tell me what happened.
Huh...?
Heard right. But you gotta skip town.
entries.maleVariant: You heard right. But you gotta skip town.

entries.femaleVariant: She's still my girl.
Skip...? What, a-and leave her like this?
She might be lying there full of tubes an' shit, but...
Oh, fuck!
Eat this!
And if your girl pulls through, won't be any good to her dead.
entries.maleVariant: And if your girl pulls through, you won't be any good to her dead.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, maybe... Maybe you're right.
Yeah, yeah... I'll go. Hey, thanks.
You can leave here in peace. My people won't give you any trouble.
